Project name : MESSAGE CENTER
Author : Ahmed Magdy Mahmoud.
Copyrights : Ahmed.Magdy40@gmail.com (2013).

Definition : 
message center is a small and closed message system, only support offline messages to only registered users (NON-email).

Features : 
* graphical emotions support.
* easy to change your theme (change theme folder-name in settings(theme) column in the database.

Installation :

1 - To install MESSAGE CENTER you need a new database so first create a database.
2 - Import /config/database_structure.sql to your database.
3 - Go to /config/database.php and change database parameters with you database information.
4 - Go to /config/paths.php and define the ABSOLUTE_PATH with the ABSOLUTE_PATH of your application.
5 - Now you can check message center out :)